[{"phelps":"AB00059","text":"## RÄNG WAKRAP ANATU KEN ATENGA RUMIN EMEL\n\nRäng wak ruing wi e kalemp Mas 2 ba 20 pora etemba.  Rukting ila, mukuma wunt ba rumbulrui wamp ti räng na nu na ti naning.  Wi e atenga ropon, min rop kont mondop itim wi e.  Nombogla rugl andang wamp na, wagl pana 15 nga mana orong na , kui wamp na wamp rondogla na amp wagl mam na bä ya räng wak rui wi ela rukurung näting.\n\nUgla nga wipip ropa ngui wa na akap king nga kum pinti mel bä wak rop, nu na räng kitim ila pinapenem emel ku nang mundu mong a uglmi rokon eteken keakagla tena wamp elpa bä numan mundi ugle e wak ramp.  Ugl kit bä numan pinti na, satan nga ugl bila nanga min e ninim ent kumpa polkon ekit teken eteken bongon tana nanga min a remnga mulguga wingti eken rup ropa ugle elpa bä ok tepa nimnga bi ila ment muglanka.","name":"RÄNG WAKRAP ANATU KEN ATENGA RUMIN EMEL","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"87ab3271-b2ed-47e1-b653-5e609363c786","translations":[{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"Hindi"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"kgf","lang_name":"Kube"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"}]},{"phelps":"AB06012","text":"## WAMB DOIMB RUNDING ENGA ATANGE E\n\nO Anatu O!   Nem wamb ti ken kapalga mon!  Anatu Nem tip mumukrui kona enga ami.  Wamb bä kin wintinga rupinti ela moromen wamb rondolg bä kin tek rapandanna eel etik int pentek elepa elepa ami mel molk, Anatu nga wamb numan ulg E kin mulg kona enga ik doimbrui rangal pii ela mai taing.  Anatu O!  Nem wamb nga tip rapandi Wä, wamp polgop kan ti wä, kona kui waka na, komonga na, kona kolg na, kona kui na, num kota na, kona bila Nem mondok pilik, tik mumukrui nga rondolg e kin mulunga wingti nga keipuka ela nga wi reng.  Ama kopa, Nem ama Wu rondolg wei Nem we mungrui, Nem wu pilip kuingti, Nem mung kini Wä.","name":"WAMB DOIMB RUNDING ENGA ATANGE E","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"80417675-8752-48ea-bd55-b8e17ef6a1c2","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"gu","lang_name":"Gujarati"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"}]},{"phelps":"AB07158","text":"## WAMP ON ITENG ATENGA E\n\nYa eia, Baha'i nga ik tengpi atenga wingti e wamp pora tek rakdok molk wei.  Wamp on e angtinangti molk ken wamp tenta ti ent wanka, wamp we pora angelek molk kumtei.  Wamp kolom e amp dam, ya ik mong kägl “nemnga kentmant wä enga kangem” e kelken “nemnga kentmant amp enga bäglam kentamant ampe” i nei.\n\nNanga Anatu, Ya eia, nemnga kentmant wä e, nimnga kentmant wä enga kangem e, nim mondep pelepa, nimnga ugl bä kantepa kon etepa, nin tepa olong ngopa, mel we bä pora tepa bugl ngorom.  Nim wamp numa weng doromen bä keen numan weng doron.\n\nNim wi mugl kona ila numan wengdui ugl a mim kota mel kapolga muglanga wamp bä nga nit bä penteken kelekon pund mong bä panda rokon eten ni mel a wamp e eteken ti.  Numan weng dokon kond kolkon ninim rukurung ti.  Nimng wamp kond kul ugl a mugl mai ragl napi ken pitim.  Wä Anatu we ti namboromen, nim mendepogl.  Wamp numan wengdui wate wamp kingui wä e nim mendopolg.\n\nAtenga rom wamp ent, a ik mong e nempa etanga Alláh-u-Abhá.  Ya mana kigl wema 19 etanga.\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá!\n\nTen pora kopa Anatu rop potdenmon.  (19)\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá!\n\nTen pora kopa Anatunga koemp ketal rumagli penemon.  (19)\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá!\n\nTen pora kopa Anatu ken mundu mong e ngonomen.  (19)\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá!\n\nTen pora kopa Anatunga bi paka ronomon.(19)\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá!\n\nTen pora kopa Anatu ken aenge nenemon.(19)\n\nAlláh-u-Abhá!\n\nTen pora kopa Anatu ken raka nemp moromon.(19)","name":"WAMP ON ITENG ATENGA E","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"566f5e4f-5612-4628-b40f-6f3e1f5979e5","translations":[{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"sne","lang_name":"Bau Bidayuh"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fo","lang_name":"Faroese"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ha","lang_name":"Hausa"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"Hindi"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"naq","lang_name":"Khoekhoegowab"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"ksd","lang_name":"Kuanua"},{"language":"kgf","lang_name":"Kube"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mr","lang_name":"Marathi"},{"language":"mh","lang_name":"Marshallese"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"vi","lang_name":"Vietnamese"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"AB10714","text":"## KANG AMPÄGLA BÄNGA ATENGA\n\nAnutu O, na nombolga bä wakadui:  Nanga mundmong enga lamb ela rängalg ngana na ent mipil mel kapälga mulgeimp.  Ama Nem pilip kungti wä ama rondolg wei.","name":"KANG AMPÄGLA BÄNGA ATENGA","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"af2a2e31-722b-4fd9-8d44-89ef9ef989e8","translations":[{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"naq","lang_name":"Khoekhoegowab"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"}]},{"phelps":"BB00015","text":"## NOMBOLGA ORADUI ENGA ATENGA E\n\nNanga wuta Anatu O!  Neminga numan ngoron wamb tik rapandana, Nemnga miti ela rondolg pok molgok, Neminga mul ulg e pep rok, Nemnga miti ela rondolg pok milging.  Neminga numan wengdui ulg e wamb bä ngana, wamb ent unduk pilik etim bä wakrok Nem wamb räp eten enga ralgang e pep reing.  Nem ama rondolg wei, wamb numan ngui, mel ti nga mondinadarem, kem ngui Wa, koma pou ralg ti, rondolgpi, Nem mel bä kakana mul Wä.","name":"NOMBOLGA ORADUI ENGA ATENGA E","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"1e738911-67b8-4823-8d4d-70d239e2c1e6","translations":[{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"cs","lang_name":"Czech"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"}]},{"phelps":"BB00554","text":"## MUKULMÄ WINTNGA ATENGA\n\nNanga Anatu O!  Na nem nga ki kaemb ela rot nemb kai mondond.  Wamb ti ent nem nga palga e kandep tepa elem rukur ela malanga nenem ent räp indam kapälga etemba.  Wamb e nem nga mangä porombel ela maglanka nem nga rondolg ent räp itin.  Nanga mund mong e rokon rängalg mundi, Anatu O, nem nga rängalg kiyakalga ti ent na rokon rutdun ent nenem etiken motdon.  Nem nga wamb numan ngui ulg ela, nem nga mukama rangagl kai ent nanga king kalg rangagl ngokon ku eten.","name":"MUKULMÄ WINTNGA ATENGA","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"41e037f5-980b-4a8a-9fc4-070ffaa29bdc","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"}]},{"phelps":"BH00009SER","text":"## NOMBALGA ÄNDING ENGA ATENGA\n\nNa Neminga, mondopa pili ela rot niti nanga Anatu O, Nem kin pora mondop pilip nanga mangä kona wak rund, na nanam Niminga kii kaimb ela tep int.  Enga numan wengdui, tepa mumukrui kona ela, Nemnga memb e na mana dokon ngana nangkona kai mint wiibm.  Nem na tik rapdelgna nanga numan bä Nem räkräk ngulgmba räp eten E mel ku.  Anatu elepa ti mon, Nem tenta, wamb tiken kapälga mon, melbä na ulg na bä Nem pilik pora doron.  Nem wä pilipa kungti.","name":"NOMBALGA ÄNDING ENGA ATENGA","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"3b98e42e-d911-4cf2-a713-dc1ae8cb75ed","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"naq","lang_name":"Khoekhoegowab"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"cnr","lang_name":"Montenegrin"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"kj","lang_name":"Oshikwanyama"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"se","lang_name":"Sami"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH00074BLE","text":"## ANATU TEK OUDUI ENGA ATENGA E\n\nAnatu nga numan wengdui ulg e kona kelkel bila pora tetem, mawaga, kona na kona peng na, wamb mund mong na, komunga na, mo kona na, ku mangä na, kona kolg na, mui mam na, mui kel na, kona palga rukorong kep, bilia Anatu nga bi tek, elmnga kaip ninti ulg e ambalg palgk etimin.","name":"ANATU TEK OUDUI ENGA ATENGA E","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"30dee589-718c-4564-965a-846dc34506c5","translations":[{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bla","lang_name":"Blackfoot"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"km","lang_name":"Central Khmer"},{"language":"chr","lang_name":"Cherokee"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"dgz","lang_name":"Daga"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"gwi","lang_name":"Gwich'in"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"hur","lang_name":"Halkomelem"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"ik","lang_name":"Inupiaq"},{"language":"ga","lang_name":"Irish"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kiw","lang_name":"Kiwai"},{"language":"ksd","lang_name":"Kuanua"},{"language":"kgf","lang_name":"Kube"},{"language":"lkt","lang_name":"Lakota"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"lut","lang_name":"Lushootseed"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"moh","lang_name":"Mohawk"},{"language":"meu","lang_name":"Motu"},{"language":"nv","lang_name":"Navajo"},{"language":"ttm","lang_name":"Northern Tutchone"},{"language":"oj","lang_name":"Ojibwe"},{"language":"one","lang_name":"Oneida"},{"language":"pap","lang_name":"Papiamento"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"se","lang_name":"Sami"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"shh","lang_name":"Shoshoni"},{"language":"slh","lang_name":"Sliammon"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH01313NAM","text":"## KUI MÄN ATENGA\n\nNanga Anatu O, Nemnga bi ent na etepa tetim.  Wete Neme pilip ko mund dam, Nem pili ugl ent na män ropa tetim.  Nem ken nondopa muil ulg mint pent.  Na Nem numan ngor ulg e, e nanga rup wamb.  Nem na kond koron ulg e, ent na etepa tetim.  Nem na kond koron ulg ent nanga kui bä makrapa na etepa rondolg monodopa etim.  Akap ya mui kona ela ken weta wi mulg kona ele ken.  E ama kopa.  Nem ent na mel kai bä ngoron.  Nem, ama kopa, Wu nuim, ulg bä pora piliken, ulga bä pora pilik kongnteken eten.","name":"KUI MÄN ATENGA","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"d22ae6ba-bd48-4679-88a3-87934467c27f","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bla","lang_name":"Blackfoot"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ceb","lang_name":"Cebuano"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"chn","lang_name":"Chinook Jargon"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"cs","lang_name":"Czech"},{"language":"dgz","lang_name":"Daga"},{"language":"dak","lang_name":"Dakota"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fo","lang_name":"Faroese"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"},{"language":"ht","lang_name"