},{"language":"sl","lang_name":"Slovenian"},{"language":"st","lang_name":"Southern Sotho"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH08013","text":"## RUMBULG RUI ENGA ATENGA E\n\nWä Nuim O!  Na Nemnga tep mumuk ropa, tenta iti ulg eya tip oldong ngolgmba Neminga wamb numan ngui ul ent na tepa wangaräm.  Wä Nuim O, Nem ent Neminga rangalg E na ngana ya akap kona rumbulg mam ronom ela nemnga rangalg E kanda kinimb.  Nem ent wamb numan ngui ulg e wak rana na tamba nanga numan orong ying ying etanga.  Nuim ye, Nemnga wi e kumtemb, Nemnga mulg kona peng mumuk e kumba tana ulg kiyakalga tibä nga rangalg e kanamb.  Nemnga ulg kai bä ent na rukur tanka.  E ama kupa.  Nem ent mel bä pora ngoron.  Nem wamb bä kond kolgon. Wamb bä nga nit bä pentik keten ko.","name":"RUMBULG RUI ENGA ATENGA E","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"729ade27-fa55-4dce-8ff6-b41f793547d6","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ceb","lang_name":"Cebuano"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"F