":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"},{"language":"vi","lang_name":"Vietnamese"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"## TENGDUI ATENGA KINTINGA\n\nAtenga kägl ant keng orong pomena, Bahá’í wamp pora tenta tenta nek näi.  Koemp keta na ki na pora uglumi rokon Bahá’u’lláh nga alta morom illa koemp keta orong dokon molkon atenga rui.\n\nNa para dop nent, Anatu, nem ent na mim eteken, na peliken kandaken i eten ni na nim rop potontip neken.  Nanga rondogl ti mon.  Na wa koropa ent nem wa nuim rondogl we eken para dop nent.  Na tikipugli bä nga tepa rapundi wä e.","name":"TENGDUI ATENGA KINTINGA","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"251cc583-bd0a-41ca-9e34-f3c462a502c2","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"am","lang_name":"Amharic"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"sne","lang_name":"Bau Bidayuh"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"km","lang_name":"Central Khmer"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"chn","lang_name":"Chinook Jargon"},{"language":"co","lang_name":"Corsican"},{"language":"cr","lang_name":"Cree"},{"language":"dgz","lang_name":"Daga"},{"language":"dak","lang_name":"Dakota"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"fo","lang_name":"Faroese"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fij